the%20ongoing%20crisis.%20Union%20ministers%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh%20were%20also%20present%20for%20the%20meeting%2C%20but%20no%20officials%20from%20the%20Centre%20or%20the%20state%20attended%20it%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20underscoring%20its%20exclusivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20comes%20amid%20massive%20Opposition%20pressure%20on%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20alleged%20silence%20on%20Manipur.%20Slogans%20of%20Manipur%20had%20rent%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20the%20Opposition%20interrupted%20PM%20Modi's%20speech%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20following%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20joint%20address%20for%20over%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20has%20been%20especially%20focussed%20on%20Manipur%20after%20the%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20went%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20recent%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20comes%20on%20a%20day%20that%20Manipur%20governor%20Anusiya%20Uikey%20was%20removed%20and%20new%20Assam%20governor%20Lakshman%20Prasad%20Acharya%20was%20given%20additional%20charge%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20year%2C%20the%20clashes%20between%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%20--%20a%20term%20given%20by%20the%20British%20in%20colonial%20times%20--%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20that%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20want%20a%20separate%20administrative%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722191940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Flce1q17o_n-biren-singh_625x300_14_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-biren-singhs-first-face-to-face-on-manipur-violence-sources-6209737%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20a%20face-to-face%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20ongoing%20visit%20to%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-biren-singhs-first-face-to-face-on-manipur-violence-sources-6209737%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-biren-singhs-first-face-to-face-on-manipur-violence-sources-6209737%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-biren-singhs-first-face-to-face-on-manipur-violence-sources-6209737%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCome%20Up%2C%20Quick%26quot%3B%3A%20Video%20Shows%20Students%20Rushing%20Out%20Of%20Delhi%20Coaching%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20horrifying%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%20when%20water%20gushed%20into%20its%20basement%20-%20being%20used%20as%20a%20library%20in%20violation%20of%20rules.%20Several%20students%20were%20trapped%20and%20three%20died%20in%20the%20waterlogged%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%2C%20seemingly%20shot%20hours%20before%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20three%20students%20were%20recovered%2C%20shows%20many%20students%20rushing%20out%20of%20the%20flooded%20basement%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20in%20west%20Delhi%20Rajendra%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20was%20gushing%20down%20the%20stairs%20as%20the%20students%20waded%20through%20water%2C%20it%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20man%20can%20be%20heard%20asking%20the%20students%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20basement%20quickly.%20%26quot%3BKids%2C%20come%20up%20quickly.%20Quick%2C%20quick...%20Is%20anyone%20left%20behind%3F%20Is%20anyone%20down%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20students%20-%20Tania%20Soni%20(25)%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%20(25)%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%20(28)%20-%20were%20indeed%20left%20behind%20and%20their%20bodies%20were%20recovered%20after%20a%20seven-hour%20long%20rescue%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20they%20received%20a%20call%20about%20waterlogging%20from%20the%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Centre%20around%207%20pm%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20police%20are%20probing%20the%20cause%20behind%20the%20flooding%2C%20locals%20blame%20the%20poor%20drainage%20system%20in%20the%20area.%20They%20say%20it%20was%20heavily%20clogged%20with%20silt%20and%20overflowed%20leading%20to%20a%20flood-like%20situation%20following%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20showed%20the%20road%20in%20front%20of%20the%20coaching%20institute%20severely%20waterlogged%20with%20waist-deep%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20registered%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20and%20formed%20multiple%20teams%20to%20probe%20the%20incident.%20The%20investigations%20so%20far%20have%20indicated%20multiple%20lapses%20on%20the%20part%20of%20its%20owner%20and%20civic%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Fire%20Services%20chief%20Atul%20Garg%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20option%20to%20de-water%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-storey%20coaching%20centre%20for%20the%20preparation%20of%20civil%20services%20had%20its%20building%20plan%20approved%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20department%20in%202021%20by%20falsely%20showing%20that%20it%20was%20being%20used%20as%20a%20store%20room%2C%20as%20per%20the%20building%20plan%20and%20the%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%20of%20the%20fire%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20building%20has%20fire%20NOC%2C%20but%20in%20the%20NOC%20they%20had%20shown%20the%20basement%20as%20a%20store%20room.%20The%20management%20of%20the%20institute%20was%20using%20the%20same%20room%20as%20a%20classroom%20or%20library%20which%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20NOC%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20students%20stated%20protests%20to%20demand%20justice%20for%20the%20civil%20service%20aspirants%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20demanded%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20and%20compensation%20for%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20institute%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bare%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20these%20promising%20young%20individuals%20who%20were%20preparing%20to%20serve%20our%20nation%20with%20dedication%20and%20commitment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRAU's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20supporting%20the%20ongoing%20investigations%20into%20this%20tragic%20incident.%20We%20are%20cooperating%20fully%20with%20the%20relevant%20authorities%20and%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20necessary%20information%20is%20provided%20and%20that%20the%20investigation%20proceeds%20with%20the%20utmost%20diligence%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20and%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20charged%20under%20culpable%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722191700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F53gl99u_coaching-centre-basement-flooding_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fvideo-shows-students-rushing-out-as-water-gushed-into-delhi-basement-6209785%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20horrifying%20scene%20unfolded%20at%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Delhi