n%20Kovai%20Sathyan%20said%20the%20murders%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20illustrate%20the%20lawlessness%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20incompetence%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMK%20Stalin%20should%20examine%20if%20he%20has%20the%20moral%20right%20to%20continue%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20state%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20says%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20is%20far%20better%20than%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states.%20Citing%20data%20from%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%2C%20it%20has%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20playing%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20spokesperson%20Dr%20Hafeezullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20no-crime%20situation%20is%20utopian%20across%20the%20world.%20What%20is%20important%20is%20how%20the%20government%20responds%20and%20prevents.%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20has%20dealt%20with%20these%20firmly%20and%20professionally%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20workers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20involved%20in%20several%20criminal%20cases%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20murder%20and%20drugs%20cases%20and%20(party%20chief)%20Annamalai%20should%20introspect%20if%20he%20should%20continue%20as%20state%20BJP%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20BJP's%20Tamilisai%20Soundarajan%20has%20said%20the%20party%20admitted%20criminals%20without%20any%20scrutiny%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20happen%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20headed%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722184860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6fnah1tg_mk-stalin_625x300_19_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-vs-opposition-as-two-more-political-workers-from-tamil-nadu-killed-6209183%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20political%20workers%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20been%20murdered%20in%20less%20than%2024%20ho