om%2Fsimone-biles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESimone%20Biles%3C%2Fa%3E'%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20competition%20to%20prioritize%20her%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%205-foot%2C%2021-year-old%20gymnast%20from%20St.%20Paul%2C%20Minnesota%2C%20is%20known%20for%20her%20dominance%20on%20the%20uneven%20bars%20and%20the%20balance%20beam.%20Lee%20has%20earned%20three%20Olympic%20medals%2C%20including%20a%20bronze%20on%20the%20uneven%20bars%20and%20a%20silver%20in%20the%20women's%20team%20event.%20She%20later%20became%20the%20NCAA%20beam%20and%20SEC%20uneven%20bars%20champion%20while%20competing%20collegiately%20at%20Auburn%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20she%20is%20going%20for%20more%20glory%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-summer-olympics-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223190d6e0-e9bc-4569-9a21-415f3b6b70fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuni%20Lee's%20early%20life%20and%20gymnastics%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20began%20gymnastics%20as%20a%20young%20child%3B%20she%20has%20said%20she%20always%20liked%20to%20tumble%2C%20prompting%20her%20parents%20to%20buy%20her%20a%20wooden%20balance%20beam%20to%20practice%20on.%20She%20began%20formal%20training%20at%20six%20years%20old%20at%20the%20Midwest%20Gymnastics%20Center%2C%20where%20Puner%20Koy%20coached%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee's%20stardom%20was%20evident%20early%20on.%20In%20her%20second%20competition%20of%20her%20entire%20career%2C%20she%20was%20an%20all-around%20champion%20at%20a%20state%20gymnastics%20meet.%20By%20age%2011%2C%20she%20qualified%20as%20an%20elite%20athlete%20in%20the%20USA%20Gymnastics%20Women's%20Development%20Program%2C%20meaning%20she%20could%20compete%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%20international%20competitions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%2014%2C%20she%20was%20on%20the%20US%20Junior%20National%20Team.%20Two%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyears%20later%2C%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20US%20Senior%20National%20Team%2C%20she%20won%20first%20place%20on%20floor%2C%20uneven%20bars%2C%20and%20all-around%20at%20the%202019%20City%20of%20Jesolo%20Trophy%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20is%20a%20member%20of%20Minnesota's%20Hmong%20community%2C%20many%20members%20of%20whom%20settled%20in%20the%20American%20Midwest%20after%20facing%20oppression%20in%20East%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20Many%20of%20them%20became%20refugees%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20fought%20alongside%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hmong%20culture%20typically%20endorses%20academics%20over%20sports%2C%20but%20Lee's%20family%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20athleticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20debut%20at%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Games%20%E2%80%94%20which%20took%20place%20in%202021%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20Lee%20became%20the%20second%20Hmong%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20Olympics%20for%20any%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228282ecc3-50c8-4c91-9a26-9c2fea54ada0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20pivotal%20Tokyo%20Games%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20spent%20years%20admiring%20the%20most%20decorated%20gymnast%20of%20all%20time%2C%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuni-lee-simone-biles-pushed-me-best-version-of-myself-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20competed%20alongside%20Biles%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Team%20USA%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20at%20the%20Olympics%2C%20my%20coach%20and%20I%20noticed%20that%20when%20I%20worked%20alongside%20her%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20getting%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20how%20she%20does%20things%2C%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20'I%20wanna%20be%20like%20her%2C'%20so%20it%20really%20pushed%20me%20to%20be%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeam%20USA%20fans%20were%20stunned%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3