0he%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20doing%20school%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20I%20also%20took%20away%20his%20weekend%20gaming%20privileges.%20He%20ignored%20me%2C%20so%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxbox-will-speak-on-playstation-cross-platform-rumors-says-ceo-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiding%20the%20Xbox%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20my%20bed%20and%20in%20other%20places%20that%20are%20still%20a%20secret%20to%20this%20day.%20Somehow%2C%20Taylor%20always%20managed%20to%20find%20the%20gaming%20system.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20he%20was%20just%20being%20disrespectful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20I%20was%20so%20frustrated%20that%20I%20hurled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-xbox-games-of-all-time-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Xbox%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20my%20bedroom%20deck%2C%20and%20it%20crashed%20down%20from%20the%20second%20floor.%20Even%20then%20it%20didn't%20break%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20my%20boyfriend%20to%20put%20the%20Xbox%20in%20his%20trunk%20where%20Taylor%20couldn't%20get%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230719b49-b959-40ea-9a19-6169a160b665%5C%22%3ETaylor%20transferred%20to%20a%20school%20with%20an%20esports%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Taylor%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-junior-high-teacher-pay-cut-hit-student-anime-name-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejunior%20in%20high%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20boys%20transferred%20schools%2C%20mostly%20to%20play%20traditional%20athletics.%20Tyler%20plays%20football%20and%20basketball%2C%20and%20Taylor%20plays%20basketball.%20Both%20were%20hoping%20to%20leverage%20sports%20for%20college%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20came%20home%20and%20told%20me%20the%20new%20school%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-work-8-to-5-job-to-supplement-esports-c