weren't%20just%20a%20waste%20of%20time%2C%20but%20friends%20and%20family%20weren't%20convinced%20gaming%20could%20have%20real%20benefits.%20Then%2C%20Taylor%20started%20winning%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20win%20led%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20gaming%20equipment%20for%20his%20school.%20It%20was%20so%20much%20that%20the%20team%20shared%20it%20with%20two%20other%20local%20high%20schools.%20When%20Taylor%20became%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playvs.com%2Fnews%2Ffrost-2k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20national%20champion%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20won%20prize%20money%20that%20he%20could%20use%20to%20pay%20for%20books%20and%20other%20expenses%20at%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261b1707d-2f9f-4223-9a5f-dc0a300f6742%5C%22%3EI'm%20convinced%20that%20video%20games%20can%20lead%20to%20success%20for%20kids%20like%20mine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20will%20be%20a%20senior%20this%20fall%2C%20and%20he's%20looking%20at%20colleges%20that%20have%20esports%20programs.%20One%20historically%20Black%20college%2C%20Johnson%20C.%20Smith%20University%2C%20even%20has%20an%20esports%20and%20gaming%20minor.%20For%20kids%20like%20Taylor%2C%20esports%20are%20so%20much%20more%20than%20games%3A%20they're%20a%20real%20path%20forward%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20use%20something%20they're%20passionate%20about%20to%20build%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20proud%20mom.%20I%20even%20use%20the%20streaming%20platform%20Twitch%20to%20watch%20games%20that%20Taylor%20has%20played%20as%20if%20they're%20real%20sporting%20events.%20I'm%20even%20looking%20at%20starting%20a%20gaming%20club%20at%20the%20elementary%20school%20where%20I%20work%20because%20I've%20seen%20first-hand%20how%20powerful%20video%20games%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-threw-xbox-out-window-son-esports-champion-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722175682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3b60ea0fc5856d597b3fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-threw-xbox-out-window-son-esports-champion-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sherry%20Williams%20was%20worried%20about%20how%20much%20time%20her%20son%20was%20spending%20playing%20video%20games.%20He%20is%20now%20winning%20scholarships%20for%20esports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-threw-xbox-out-window-son-esports-champion-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22National%20Testing%20Agency%20Declares%20CUET%20UG%202024%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20has%20released%20the%20results%20for%20the%20Common%20University%20Entrance%20Test%2C%20Undergraduate%20(CUET%20UG)%202024%20today.%20Candidates%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%20can%20check%20their%20results%20by%20visiting%20the%20official%20CUET%20UG%20website.%20They%20will%20need%20to%20enter%20their%20login%20credentials%20to%20access%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20released%20the%20final%20answer%20key%20for%20the%20exam%20on%20July%2025.%20These%20answer%20keys%20will%20be%20used%20to%20prepare%20the%20result%2FNTA%20scores%20for%20CUET%20UG%202024.%20The%20answer%20keys%20for%20OMR-based%20exams%20are%20available%20in%20a%20219-page%20PDF%20file%2C%20while%20the%20CBT%20exam%20keys%20are%20available%20in%20a%20151-page%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CUET%20UG%20results%20were%20initially%20scheduled%20to%20be%20released%20on%20June%2030%2C%20but%20the%20NTA%20postponed%20them%20due%20to%20issues%20with%20paper%20leak%20allegations%20related%20to%20NEET-UG%2C%20UGC-NET%2C%20and%20CSIR-UGC-NET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CUET%20UG%20exam%20covered%20a%20total%20of%2061%20subjects%2C%20including%2033%20languages%2C%2027%20domain%20subjects%2C%20and%20a%20general%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20candidate%20was%20allowed%20to%20attempt%20up%20to%20six%20test%20papers%2C%20including%20four%20or%20five%20domain%20subjects%20(along%20with%20a%20general%20test)%20and%20one%20or%20two%20language%20papers.%20Candidates%20received%20five%20marks%20for%20each%20correct%20answer%2C%20with%20one%20mark%20deducted%20for%20each%20incorrect%20answer.%20Unanswered%20questions%20were%20scored%20as%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CUET%20UG%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20hybrid%20mode%20(CBT%20and%20Pen%20and%20Paper)%20on%20May%2015%2C%2016%2C%2017%2C%2018%2C%2021%2C%2022%2C%2024%2C%20and%2029%20across%20379%20cities%2C%20including%2026%20cities%20outside%20India.%20The%20CUET-UG%20exam%2C%20held%20in%20a%20hybrid%20format%2C%20was%20cancelled%20in%20Delhi%20the%20night%20before%20the%20scheduled%20date%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Blogistical%20reasons%26quot%3B%20but%20was%20later%20conducted%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2015%20subjects%2C%20exams%20were%20conducted%20in%20a%20pen-and-paper%20format%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%2048%20subjects%20were%20tested%20via%20computer-based%20testing%20(CBT).%20This%20year%2C%20over%2013.4%20lakh%20candidates%20registered%20for%20the%20test%2C%20which%20is%20used%20for%20admission%20to%20undergraduate%20courses%20in%20261%20central%2C%20state%2C%20deemed%2C%20and%20private%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2013%20lakh%20candidates%20participated%20in%20this%20session.%20The%20provisional%20answer%20key%20was%20released%20on%20July%206%2C%20following%20which%20some%20students%20raised%20objections.%20To%20address%20these%20concerns%2C%20a%20retest%20was%20conducted%20for%20about%201%2C000%20students%20on%20July%2019%2C%20and%20the%20revised%20provisional%20answer%20key%20was%20issued%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722175500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%