%20Apex%20Body%2C%20Leh%20(ABL)%20and%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%20from%20Ladakh%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20of%20demands%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Dras%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20push%20the%20government%20too%20much%20during%20the%20elections.%20We%20wanted%20to%20give%20them%20some%20breathing%20space%20after%20the%20polls%3B%20we%20were%20hopeful%20that%20the%20new%20government%20would%20take%20some%20concrete%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20they%20will%20invite%20our%20leaders%20for%20talks%20following%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20memorandum.%20If%20that%20doesn't%20happen%2C%20we%20will%20launch%20another%20round%20of%20protests%20starting%20August%2015%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20will%20start%20a%2028-day%20fast%20on%20August%2015%2C%20when%20the%20country%20will%20celebrate%20its%2078th%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wangchuk%20claimed%20the%20government%20withdrew%20its%20promise%20to%20provide%20tribal%20area%20status%20and%20full%20statehood%20to%20Ladakh%20under%20pressure%20from%20%26quot%3Bindustrialists%20who%20want%20to%20exploit%20the%20resources%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20ecologically%20fragile%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20noted%20engineer%20claimed%20that%20land%20in%20Ladakh%20is%20being%20allocated%20for%20solar%20power%20projects%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Council%20(LAHDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20powers%20of%20the%20LAHDC%20are%20being%20diluted%20and%20clearances%20are%20being%20issued%20from%20the%20top.%20That's%20why%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20are%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20320%20clear%20sunny%20days%20a%20year%20and%20an%20average%20daily%20global%20solar%20radiation%20of%202022%20kWh%2Fm%20sq%2Fannum%2C%20Ladakh%20is%20a%20solar%20power%20generation%20hotspot%20in%20India.%20The%20cold%20desert%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20generate%2035%20GW%20from%20solar%20energy%20and%20100%20GW%20from%20wind%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wangchuk%20said%20he%20is%20all%20for%20clean%20energy%20but%20%26quot%3Bthis%20should%20be%20done%20in%20a%20proper%20way%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20it%20is%20solar%20power%2C%20it%20should%20not%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20survival%20of%20local%20people%20and%20wildlife.%20We%20cannot%20take%20away%20their%20pasture%20lands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20environmentalist%20said%20the%20Modi%20government%20made%20several%20big%20announcements%20to%20deal%20with%20climate%20change%20but%20not%20much%20has%20happened%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20hopeful.%20They%20proactively%20banned%20single-use%20plastics.%20Normally%2C%20this%20happens%20when%20there%20is%20pressure%20from%20people.%20They%20declared%20Ladakh%20carbon%20neutral.%20But%20not%20much%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20government's%20climate%20commitments%20and%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20set%20a%20target%20of%20becoming%20a%20net%20zero%20economy%20by%202070%2C%20which%20is%20very%20far%20off.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%20discussions%20on%20expanding%20coal%20power%20usage.%20I%20am%20pained%20to%20see%20such%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Mr%20Wangchuk%20went%20on%20a%2021-day%20fast%2C%20surviving%20only%20on%20salt%20and%20water%2C%20to%20demand%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20its%20inclusion%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20help%20protect%20the%20ecologically%20fragile%20region%20from%20%26quot%3Bgreedy%26quot%3B%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20repeal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20Ladakh%20became%20a%20separate%20union%20territory%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20legislature%26quot%3B.%20The%20Buddhist-dominated%20Leh%20district%20had%20long%20demanded%20union%20territory%20status%20due%20to%20alleged%20neglect%20by%20the%20erstwhile%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20region%20now%20entirely%20administered%20by%20bureaucrats%2C%20many%20in%20Ladakh%20demand%20that%20the%20union%20territory%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20which%20provides%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20Autonomous%20District%20Councils%20(ADCs)%20with%20legislative%2C%20judicial%20and%20administrative%20autonomy%20within%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20councils%20administer%20areas%20under%20their%20jurisdiction%2C%20making%20laws%20on%20specific%20matters%20with%20the%20governor's%20assent.%20They%20can%20establish%20village%20councils%20or%20courts%20for%20dispute%20resolution%20and%20manage%20facilities%20and%20services%20within%20their%20areas%2C%20including%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20They%20also%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20impose%20taxes%20and%20regulate%20certain%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wangchuk%20had%20previously%20said%20that%20statehood%20and%20constitutional%20protection%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20would%20not%20impact%20defence%20and%20national%20security-related%20projects%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadakh's%20former%20MP%2C%20Jamyang%20Tsering%20Namgyal%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20had%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20region%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20to%20safeguard%20the%20land%2C%20employment%20and%20cultural%20identity%20of%20the%20local%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Union%20Tribal%20Affairs%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20promised%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20is%20required%20from%20a%20constitutional%20perspective%20to%20protect%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202019%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(NCST)%20wrote%20to%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Munda%2C%20recommending%20that%20Ladakh%20be%20declared%20a%20tribal%20area%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722174900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2so875f4_sonam-wangchuk_625x300_06_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-launch-28-day-fast-on-independence-day-if-activist-sonam-wangchuk-6208271%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Climate%20activist%20Soman%20Wangchuk%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20that%20he%20will%20launch%20a%2028-day%20fast%20on%20Independence%20Day%20if%20the%20government%20does%20not%20invite%20Ladakh%20authorities%20for%20talks%20on%20demands%20for%20statehood%20and%20constitutional%20protection%20for%20the%20union%20territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-launch-28-day-fast-on-independence-day-if-activist-sonam-wangchuk-6208271%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harris%20campaign%20'raises%20%24200m'%20in%20week%20since%20Biden%20withdrawal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722174900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-kamala-harris-election_6641425.jpg%3F20240728151212%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fkamala-harris-campaign-raises-200m-in-week-since-joe-bidens-withdrawal-13186330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kamala%20Harris's%20election%20campaign%20has%20said%20it%20raised%20%24200m%20(%C2%A3156m)%20in%20the%20week%20since%20she%20became%20a%20preside