nd-belief-in-middle-east-13186275%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuccess%20Is...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Special%20Message%20For%20Bhaker%20After%20Olympics%20Bronze%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20on%20Sunday%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20shooter%20to%20win%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20Olympics%2C%20bagging%20a%20bronze%20in%20the%2010m%20Air%20Pistol%20event%20in%20Paris%202024.%20Taking%20in%20the%20momentous%20occasion%2C%20Bhaker%20claimed%20the%20medal%20was%20long%20due%20as%20the%20country's%20shooters%20had%20fired%20blanks%20in%20the%20last%20two%20editions%20of%20the%20games%20at%20Rio%20(2016)%20and%20Tokyo%20(2020).%20The%2022-year-old%20shooter%20said%20the%20country%20%E2%80%98deserves%20even%20more%20medals.'%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20great%20and%20it%20was%20a%20medal%20long%20due%20for%20India.%20I%20was%20just%20merely%20a%20mode%20to%20do%20it%20and%20India%20deserves%20even%20more%20medals%2C%20as%20many%20as%20possible.%20We%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20as%20many%20events%20as%20possible%20this%20time.%20And%20the%20entire%20team%20has%20worked%20really%20hard.%20And%20personally%2C%20for%20me%2C%20the%20feeling%20is%20really%20surreal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manu%20soon%20after%20winning%20the%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20that%20I%20did%20a%20good%20job%2C%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%2C%20and%20even%20till%20the%20last%20shot%20I%20was%20just%20fighting%20with%20all%20the%20energy%20that%20I%20had.%20This%20was%20bronze.%20But%20I'm%20really%20grateful%20that%20I%20could%20win%2C%20maybe%20a%20better%20result%20next%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Manu%20in%20the%20post-event%20interview.%20Manu%20is%20participating%20in%20her%20second%20Olympic%20Games%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20shoot%20in%20one%20more%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lead%20the%20tributes%20for%20Bhaker%20after%20the%20historic%20Olympic%20medal%20and%20s