Indian%20contingent%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Tarun%20Tahiliani.%20%26quot%3BThis%20prestigious%20collaboration%20for%20Tasva%2C%20as%20the%20'Official%20Ceremonial%20Dress%20Partner'%20for%20Team%20India%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Tasva's%20journey%20as%20it%20represents%20the%20spirit%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20elegance%20of%20India%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20Indian%20athletes'%20ceremonial%20attire%20for%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20draws%20profound%20inspiration%20from%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20%26quot%3BThe%20tricolor%20palette%20embodies%20national%20pride%20and%20unity.%20The%20contemporary%20silhouettes%20of%20the%20Bundi%20jacket%20and%20the%20pre-pleated%20saree%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20thoughtful%20choice%20of%20fabrics-cotton%20and%20viscose%20crepe-along%20with%20practical%20detail%2C%20not%20just%20ensures%20comfort%20and%20functionality%20for%20the%20athletes%2C%20but%20also%20represents%20a%20fine%20balance%20of%20tradition%20with%20modernity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722166920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fg0i162so_indian-olympic_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparis-olympics-tarun-tahiliani-not-a-couture-show-tarun-tahiliani-to-ndtv-amid-olympics-costume-row-6207878%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Responding%20to%20the%20criticism%20of%20the%20Indian%20contingent's%20costume%20at%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20fashion%20designer%20Tarun%20Tahiliani%20has%20said%20he%20stands%20by%20the%20design%20and%20slammed%20%26quot%3Barmchair%20critics%26quot%3B%20for%20implying%20that%20he%20charged%20a%20fee%20for%20designing%20the%20athletes'%20attire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparis-olympics-tarun-tahiliani-not-a-couture-show-tarun-tahiliani-to-ndtv-a