%20professionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20supportive%20figure%20throughout%20Bhaker's%20journey%2C%20bought%20her%20a%20gun%20without%20much%20contemplation%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20has%20been%20waiving%20the%20tri-colour%20high%20at%20national%20and%20global%20events%20since%20she%20was%20a%20teenager.%20At%20the%202017%20national%20shooting%20championships%2C%20Manu%20Bhaker%20grabbed%20the%20spotlight%20as%20she%20defeated%20Olympian%20and%20former%20world%20No.%201%20Heena%20Sidhu.%20It%20was%20her%20record%20score%20of%20242.3%20that%20re-wrote%20the%20history%20books%2C%20putting%20her%20score%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20record%20books%20in%20the%2010m%20Air%20Pistol%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%202017%20Asian%20junior%20championships%20and%20it%20was%20in%202018%20that%20Manu%20announced%20her%20arrival%20at%20the%20world%20level%2C%20with%20making%20her%20debut%20in%20International%20Sport%20Shooting%20Federation%20(ISSF)%20World%20Cup%20at%20Guadalajara%2C%20breaking%20the%20junior%20world%20record%20in%20the%20qualification%20round%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2016%20years%20old%2C%20Manu%20became%20the%20youngest%20Indian%20to%20win%20a%20gold%20medal%20at%20an%20ISSF%20World%20Cup.%20Bhaker%20kept%20winning%20gold%20medals%20in%20the%20individual%20and%20mixed%20team%20event%20in%20the%2010m%20Air%20Pistol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20Australia%2C%20Manu%20Bhaker%20registered%20her%20name%20in%20history%20books%2C%20scripting%20a%20new%20Games%20record%20to%20grab%20the%20women's%2010m%20Air%20Pistol%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20also%20sealed%20her%20entry%20into%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20with%20a%20fourth-place%20finish%20at%20the%202019%20Munich%20ISSF%20World%20Cup.%20She%20then%20added%20a%20gold%20and%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%2010m%20Air%20Pistol%20at%20the%202021%20New%20Delhi%20ISSF%20World%20Cup%2C%20lifting%20the%20country's%20hopes%20of%20a%20medal%20in%20shooting%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20in%20Tokyo.%20But%2C%20a%20pistol%20malfunction%20cost%20her%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20podium%2C%20after%20Bhaker%20had%20topped%20the%20qualification%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shooter%20from%20Haryana%2C%20however%2C%20was%20keen%20to%20make%20amends%20on%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722166620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvko73n8g_cc_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-manu-bhaker-indias-star-shooter-who-made-history-at-paris-olympics-2024-6206002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paris%20Olympics%202024%3A%20Manu%20Bhaker%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20from%20India%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20in%20shooting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-manu-bhaker-indias-star-shooter-who-made-history-at-paris-olympics-2024-6206002%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-manu-bhaker-indias-star-shooter-who-made-history-at-paris-olympics-2024-6206002%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-manu-bhaker-indias-star-shooter-who-made-history-at-paris-olympics-2024-6206002%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PSU%20banks%20may%20get%20another%202-year%20extension%20to%20comply%20with%20Sebi's%20MPS%20norms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722166417000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1718996383-4234.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fpsu-banks-may-get-another-2-year-extension-to-comply-with-sebi-s-mps-norms-124072800266_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(Sebi)%2C%20all%20listed%20companies%20must%20maintain%20an%20MPS%20of%2025%25%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fpsu-banks-may-get-another-2-year-extension-to-comply-with-sebi-s-mps-norms-124072800266_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fpsu-banks-may-get-another-2-year-extension-to-comply-with-sebi-s-mps-norms-124072800266_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fpsu-banks-may-get-another-2-year-extension-to-comply-with-sebi-s-mps-norms-124072800266_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manu%20Reveals%20How%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20Helped%20Her%20Win%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20Medal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20etched%20her%20name%20in%20the%20golden%20pages%20of%20Indian%20sporting%20history%20on%20Sunday%20as%20she%20became%20the%20Indian%20woman%20shooter%20to%20win%20an%20Olympics%20medal.%20A%20resilient%20Manu%20Bhaker%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20shooter%20to%20claim%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20by%20snaring%20a%20bronze%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%20in%20Paris%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20triumph%20that%20opened%20the%20country's%20account%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games%20and%20ended%20a%2012-year%20wait%20for%20its%20much-hyped%20shooters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20India%20won%20shooting%20medals%20at%20the%20Olympics%20was%20in%202012%20London%20edition%20where%20rapid-fire%20pistol%20shooter%20Vijay%20Kumar%20and%2010m%20air%20rifle%20marksman%20Gagan%20Narang%20clinched%20silver%20and%20bronze%20respectively.%20Narang%20is%20the%20chef%20de%20mission%20of%20the%20Paris%20contingent%20right%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20long%20due%20medal%20for%20India.%20I%20was%20merely%20a%20mode%20to%20do%20it.%20India%20deserves%20even%20more%20medals.%20We%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20(winning)%20as%20many%20medals%20as%20possible%20this%20time.%20Personally%20for%20me%20the%20feeling%20is%20surreal.%20I%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort.%20Even%20till%20the%20last%20shot%20I%20was%20fighting%20with%20all%20energy%20that%20I%20had.%20This%20is%20a%20bronze.%20Maybe%20better%20next%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20Bhaker%20said%20after%20the%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20last%20few%20moments%20of%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20final.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20Gita%2C%20so%20what%20was%20going%20through%20my%20mind%20is%20'just%20do%20what%20you%20are%20meant%20to%20do%2C%20do%20what%20you%20are%20supposed%20to%20do'%20and%20leave%20whatever.%20Destiny%20you%20can't%20control.%20So%2C%20in%20Gita%2C%20Krishna%20says%20to%20Arjun%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20focus%20on%20the%20Karma%2C%20and%20not%20on%20the%20outcome.%20That%20was%20running%20in%20my%20head%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Tokyo%20I%20was%20very%20disappointed.%20It%20took%20a%20long%20time%20to%20recover%20form%20that.%20The%20past%20is%20in%20the%20past%2C%20let's%20just%20focus%20on%20the%20present.%20This%20medal%20its%20a%20team%20work%20always.%20I%20am%20really%20happy%20I%20was%20a%20medium%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722166260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fgofnd83o_manu-bhaker-shooting_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Fmanu-bhaker-reveals-how-bhagavad-gita-helped-her-win-indias-first-medal-at-paris-olympics-2024-6207686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20resilient%20Manu%20Bhaker%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20shooter%20to%20claim%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20by%20snaring%20a%20bronze%20in%20the%2010