.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67307858.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67307858.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP's%20Veteran%20Haribhau%20Kisanrao%20Bagde%20Named%20Rajasthan%20Governor%3A%205%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-droupadi-murmu-appoints-new-governors-in-9-states-6205341%5C%22%3EDroupadi%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20appointed%20former%20Maharashtra%20Speaker%20and%20veteran%20BJP%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frajasthan.ndtv.in%2Frajasthan-news%2Frajasthan-new-governor-who-is-haribhau-kisanrao-bagde-who-was-made-the-new-governor-of-rajasthan-6205594%5C%22%3EHaribhau%20Kisanrao%20Bagde%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20new%20Governor%20of%20Rajasthan.%20Haribhau%20Bagde%20has%20replaced%20Kalraj%20Mishra%20whose%20tenure%20ended%20on%20July%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20being%20named%20as%20Rajasthan%20governor%2C%20Mr%20Bagde%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20me%20yesterday%20informing%20me%20that%20I%20would%20have%20to%20go%20out%20of%20Maharashtra.%20He%20also%20asked%20me%20to%20not%20reveal%20it%20to%20anyone...I%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20since%20I%20was%2012-13%20and%20completed%20its%20three-year%20course.%20Till%201980%20I%20was%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sangh.%20I%20like%20taking%20up%20challenges.%20I%20may%20have%20been%20chosen%20for%20this%20post%20because%20of%20my%20work%20in%20the%20party%20for%20so%20may%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20facts%20about%20Haribhau%20Bagde%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHaribhau%20Bagde%2C%20fondly%20called%20Nana%20by%20his%20supporters%2C%20was%20born%20on%20August%2017%2C%201945%2C%20in%20Phulamri%20taluka%20of%20then%20Aurangabad%20(Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Nagar).%20He%20was%20born%20into%20a%20poor%20farmer%20family.%20Mr%20Bagde%20sold%20newspapers%20for%20many%20years.%20He%20could%20attend%20school%20only%20up%20to%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2078-year-old%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20since%20his%20teenage%20years.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20him%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201985%2C%20and%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Aurangabad%20East%20seat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20coalition%20came%20to%20power%20in%201995%2C%20Haribhau%20Bagde%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20Minister%20for%20the%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20five-time%20MLA%2C%20he%20won%20the%202014%20Assembly%20elections%20against%20Kalyan%20Kale%20of%20the%20Congress%20from%20Phulambri.%20He%20again%20won%20the%202019%20elections%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20formed%20its%20first%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%202014%2C%20Haribhau%20Bagde%20was%20appointed%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Assembly.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20Speaker%20in%20the%20state%20from%20BJP.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722162120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F66lbdgt_haribhau-kisanrao-bagde_625x300_28_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-veteran-haribhau-kisanrao-bagde-named-rajasthan-governor-5-points-6207173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20has%20appointed%20former%20Maharashtra%20Speaker%20and%20veteran%20BJP%20leader%20Haribhau%20Kisanrao%20Bagde%20as%20the%20new%20Governor%20of%20Rajasthan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-veteran-haribhau-kisanrao-bagde-named-rajasthan-governor-5-points-6207173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-veteran-haribhau-kisanrao-bagde-named-rajasthan-governor-5-p