A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ranjan%20Mondol%2C%20a%20former%20%3Cem%3Egram%20pradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(head)%2C%20the%20group%20has%20planted%20around%205%2C00%2C000%20mangrove%20saplings%20covering%20100%20hectares%20in%20Jharkhali%20village%20of%20the%20delta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20in%20India%20are%20distributed%20across%20nine%20states%20and%20three%20union%20territories%20with%20West%20Bengal%20having%20the%20highest%20mangrove%20cover%20of%202%2C114%20sq%20km.%20Observing%20how%20places%20with%20less%20vegetation%20were%20easily%20inundated%2C%20Biswas%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352436%2Fmangrove-plantation-sundarbans-afforestation-conservation-south-parganas-west-bengal-cyclone-blind-activist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangroves%20as%20the%20only%20hope%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shrubs%20act%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%20against%20flooding%20and%20waves%20during%20cyclones%2C%20he%20notes.%20In%202005%2C%20he%20started%20to%20plant%20mangroves%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Bidyadhari%20River%20and%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20the%20local%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20confident%20of%20their%20approach%2C%20it%20was%20in%20May%202021%20that%20they%20saw%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20efforts%20when%20Cyclone%20Yaas%20hit%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20cyclone%5D%20inundated%20several%20coastal%20villages%20in%20the%20Sundarbans.%20However%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20breach%20the%20river%20banks%20nor%20did%20it%20render%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Jharkhali%20homeless%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20low-lying%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%2C%20director%20at%20Action%20for%20Protection%20of%20Wild%20Animals%20in%20Odisha%20planted%20a%20mangrove%20forest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358683%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%2C%20director%20at%20Action%20for%20Protection%20of%20Wild%20Animals%20in%20Odisha%20planted%20a%20mangrove%20forest%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bijay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20technology%20can%20withstand%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20climate.%20Only%20nature%20can%20protect%20us%20from%20such%20devastation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%2C%20who%20identifies%20as%20an%20environmentalist%2C%20points%20out.%20The%20Odisha%20native%20made%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20Badakot%20village%20in%202008%20and%20was%20shocked%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20about%20300%20meters%20across%20the%202%20km%20coastal%20stretch%20had%20disappeared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%E2%80%99s%20plight%20was%20not%20in%20isolation.%20As%20Kabi%20probed%20further%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20many%20villages%20along%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20coastline%20were%20victims%20of%20a%20similar%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20worse%20%E2%80%94%20fate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20help%2C%20Kabi%20noted%20that%20geosynthetic%20tubes%20were%20installed%20to%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%20along%20the%20boundaries.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20even%20this%20could%20not%20stop%20the%20calamity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%2015%20years%20since%20he%20decided%20to%20devote%20his%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250802%2Fodisha-mangrove-planting-save-forest-village-cyclone-stop-how-bijay-kumar-kabi-environment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangrove%20conservation%20and%20planting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20restored%20mangroves%20on%2014%20acres%20at%20Jagannathpur%20village%2C%2015%20acres%20at%20Padmanavpur%2C%2025%20acres%20in%20Badkot%2C%2010%20acres%20at%20Dibakarpur%20in%20Kendrapada%20district%2C%20and%2010%20acres%20at%20Kankana%20village%20in%20Jagatsinghpur%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Kandal%20Rajan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kandal%20Rajan%20has%20planted%20mangroves%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKandal-1721985731-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKandal%20Rajan%20has%20planted%20mangroves%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20Kannur%20district%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Kandal%20Rajan%20(%3Cem%3Ekandal%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20nickname%20which%20translates%20to%20mangrove)%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20restore%20the%20mangrove%20cover%20along%20the%20Pazhayangadi%20River.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20decades%20but%20Rajan%E2%80%99s%20spark%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20dimmed%20one%20bit.%20He%20comes%20from%20a%20long%20line%20of%20fisherfolk%20and%20says%20this%20has%20given%20him%20an%20insight%20into%20how%20ecosystems%20are%20critical%20to%20the%20fishing%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20witnessed%20their%20degradation%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277743%2Ffisherman-canoe-mangrove-conservation-nursery-kerala-kandal-rajan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20mangroves%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20the%20breeding%20ground%20for%20fish%20and%20several%20other%20marine%20and%20non-marine%20species.%20I%20have%20seen%20around%2022%20species%20of%20mangroves%20in%20these%20regions%2C%20but%20now%20most%20of%20them%20have%20disappeared%20mainly%20due%20to%20human%20intervention.%20They%20are%20being%20extensively%20cut%20down%20for%20shrimp%20or%20paddy%20cultivation.%20So%2C%20the%20least%20I%20can%20do%20is%20to%20plant%20more%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20he%20has%20planted%201%2C50%2C000%20mangroves%20while%2